'''索拉罗山'''（Monte Solaro）是[[意大利|意大利]][[坎帕尼亚大区|坎帕尼亚大区]][[卡普里岛|卡普里岛]]的最高峰，海拔589米。其陡崖形成该岛东西两侧之间的阻隔。<ref name="Maiuri1956">{{cite book|last=Maiuri|first=Amedeo|title=Capri: its history and its monuments|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=ew8MAQAAIAAJ|accessdate=4 July 2012|year=1956|publisher=Istituto Poligrafico dello Stato, Libreria dello Stato|page=15}}</ref> 
<ref name="ValdesFabbri2009">{{cite book|last1=Valdes|first1=Giuliano|last2=Fabbri|first2=Patrizia|last3=Lewis|first3=Rhiannon|title=Capri|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=GVdKpHjdkLMC&pg=PA5|accessdate=4 July 2012|date=May 2009|publisher=Casa Editrice Bonechi|isbn=978-88-476-0785-9|page=5}}</ref> 
[[File:Statue_of_Emperor_Augustus_Capri.jpg|thumb]]
大港（Marina Grande）就在山脚下。由于它罗曼蒂克的位置，可看到第勒尼安海的西北, 那不勒斯湾广阔美丽的景色，颇受画家的青睐<ref name="as)1839">{{cite book|last=as)|first=Antoine Claude Pasquin Valery (known|title=Historical, Literary, and Artistic Travels in Italy: A Complete and Methodical Guide for Travellers and Artists|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=pazp4xUh95gC&pg=PA486|accessdate=4 July 2012|year=1839|publisher=Baudry|page=486}}</ref><ref name="Britain)1856">{{cite book|author=Royal Geographical Society (Great Britain)|title=A Gazetteer of the World: Or, Dictionary of Geographical Knowledge, Compiled from the Most Recent Authorities, and Forming a Complete Body of Modern Geography -- Physical, Political, Statistical, Historical, and Ethnographical|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=grENAAAAQAAJ&pg=PA240|accessdate=4 July 2012|year=1856|publisher=A. Fullarton|page=240}}</ref>。山上有最早登陆卡普里岛的[[奥古斯都|奥古斯都]]皇帝的雕像。山上的碉堡"Fortino di Bruto"曾在19世纪初英国和法国之间的战斗中使用<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.capri.net/en/s/mount-solaro-cetrella|title=Mount Solaro - Cetrella|publisher=Capri.net|accessdate=4 July 2012}}</ref>。
